me.bhop.bjdautilities

Class ReactionMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dv8tion.jda.api.hooks.ListenerAdapter
      • me.bhop.bjdautilities.menu.ReactionMenu
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.dv8tion.jda.api.hooks.EventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReactionMenu.GuildReactionMenu, ReactionMenu.PrivateMessageReactionMenu

    public abstract class ReactionMenu
extends net.dv8tion.jda.api.hooks.ListenerAdapter
    A chat menu created from reactions (emotes). This can be used for fetching a user decision given a number of choices, or simply for something like a refreshable and persistent message. This class has no functionality, a ReactionMenu.GuildReactionMenu or ReactionMenu.PrivateMessageReactionMenu should be used instead.
